Package oracle.adf.view.rich.component

Class Summary
UIXCalendar A UIXCalendar component is an abstraction for a calendar component that shows activities by day, week, month, list.
UIXDialog A UIXDialog component is an abstraction for a container component that can deliver DialogEvents, which indicate that an action has occurred in the dialog.
UIXInputPopup The UIXInputPopup component is an abstraction for components that allow both input and selection from a list of possible values.
UIXPopup A UIXPopup component is an abstraction for a container component that shows popups.
UIXQuery Events:
UIXQuery.InternalQueryBean This class is used internally by the query component to setup ValueExpressions for its 'value' and 'model' properties when none is provided.
